  <brief_title>The CBF Study Evaluating the Effect of Betahistine on the Cerebral Blood Flow</brief_title>
  <acronym>CBF</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Parallel-Group, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Pilot Study to Evaluate the Effect of Betahistine on Cerebral Blood Flow and Gait in Subjects at Risk of Falling</official_title>
  <sponsors>
